WEBVTT

00:01.839 --> 00:03.524
<i>Previously on</i> Manhattan...

00:04.920 --> 00:07.366
You're free to walk away from
this Hill anytime you like.

00:07.720 --> 00:11.042
Just because there may be a consequence,
doesn't mean you have no choice.

00:11.400 --> 00:14.051
- He touched me.
- What do you mean he touched you?

00:14.800 --> 00:15.801
Stop it.

00:15.880 --> 00:19.726
He groped me and said something
about how he sees what you're doing,

00:19.800 --> 00:21.643
and he's waiting for you to slip up.

00:21.720 --> 00:23.051
Are you ready to start working?

00:23.120 --> 00:25.009
Keep working on implosion for Frank?

00:25.080 --> 00:27.401
- Are you gonna invite me in?
- I'm fresh out of whiskey.

00:31.080 --> 00:32.923
Who was that,
a Christmas caroler?

00:33.040 --> 00:35.850
No, just a soldier looking for a good time.

00:35.920 --> 00:37.331
It's all poisoned.

00:39.360 --> 00:40.486
<i>Our clothes?</i>

00:40.600 --> 00:43.080
Everything. It's all radioactive.

00:43.800 --> 00:45.689
<i>Command calls him Magpie.</i>

00:45.760 --> 00:47.000
He has credible intelligence

00:47.080 --> 00:49.526
their atomic program
is two months ahead of ours.

